{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["🧬 Core version: 1.10.0"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thus if a component need to change for example its "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", and if a "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component token","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" is used for it, then only the value of this "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"token","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" should be changed without any modification on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component"}]},{"text":" definition.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Components","type":"text"}]},{"text":" use ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"component tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":" exposed through the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" thanks to token providers to get their style values.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Components tokens are defined and gathered inside ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift protocol","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to be exposed then through implementation of "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to dedicated tokens providers."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because we choose to split responsabilities and objects into their own modules, we faced troubles to make possible for children themes or providers to override properties declared in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"protocols"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and defined in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"extensions","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is the reason why tokens are exposed as "},{"code":"@objc open","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to be available and overridable anywhere."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Example with ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Declare some component tokens for buttons with properties they must apply","public protocol ButtonComponentTokens {","    var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { get }","    var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { get }","    var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { get }","    var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticToken { get }","    var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { get }","}","","\/\/ There is an existing provider for such tokens","open class OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider { }","","\/\/ Define the components tokens exposed through the theme thanks to provider","extension OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","    \/\/ Raw tokens can be used","","    @objc open var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","    ","    \/\/ And also semantic tokens","","    @objc open var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThicker }","    @objc open var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusMedium }","    @objc open var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    @objc open var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ This provider is then exposed through OUDSTheme as an AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"How-to-use-component-tokens","text":"How to use component tokens","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In fact, the component tokens are declared and gathered in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" so as to force any theme to implement them, and also to allow any theme to expose such properties whathever the implementation of the theme is, across providers.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" have for values ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"raw tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"semantic tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", and in the end for values primitive types, and all these tokens are declared with ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"type aliases","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" refering all together, you can handle a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" directly in your view because the final value will be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus, get the theme and call the needed property with some helpers.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct SomeView: View {","","    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme \/\/ Supposed you used in your root view the `OUDSThemeableView` to register the theme","    @Environment(\\.colorScheme) private var colorScheme","","    var body: some View {","        Button {","            \/\/ Some action","        } label: {","            Text(\"Some label\")","                .cornerRadius(theme.button.borderRadius)","        }","        .padding(.leading, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronStart)","        .padding(.trailing, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd)","        .background(theme.button.colorBgStrongEnabledMono)","        .overlay(","            RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius: theme.button.borderRadius)","                .stroke(Color.blue, lineWidth: theme.button.borderWidthDefault)","        )","    }","\/*","    - The theme provides border semantic tokens \"borderRadius\" and \"borderWidthDefault\"","    - The theme provides a color semantic token \"colorBgStrongEnabledMono\"","    - The theme provides spaces semantic token \"spacePaddingInlineChevronStart\" and \"spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd\"","*\/","}","","\/\/ Do not forget in your app to use the `OUDSThemeableView` for your theme, e.g. `OrangeTheme`","@main","struct DesignToolbox: App {","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","                ...","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The components tokens are wrapped in tokens provider acessible through the themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Components tokens provider","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target component"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"bar","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For bars components like bottom and navigation bars"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For badges like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For buttons like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bulletList"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For list of elements with bullets"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkbox"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For checkboxes like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSCheckbox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and their indeterminate variants","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For chips like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSFilterChip"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"controlItem","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Shared and used for switch, checkbox and radio items layouts","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"divider"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For dividers like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSVerticalDivider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"icon"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For components containing icons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For links like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"pinCodeInput","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"quantityInput","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radioButton"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Fo